.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-PAYMENT-COUNT" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-payment-count \- show payment count by status
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-payment-count
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns counts of payments grouped by status (complete, failed, pending).
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"total":N, "complete":N, "failed":N, "pending":N}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-payment-summary (1),
.BR lightning-payment-list-failed (1)
